00:53:31,280 --> 00:53:32,719
[SPEAKER_00] društvenim koje mislim da su štetne.

674
00:53:32,719 --> 00:53:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] Otvoreno ću reći što vjerujem ili ne vjerujem

675
00:53:35,960 --> 00:53:37,739
[SPEAKER_00] i ono, Bruno na kavi sa frendovima

676
00:53:37,739 --> 00:53:39,340
[SPEAKER_00] je isti on je Bruno u emisiji

677
00:53:39,340 --> 00:53:41,280
[SPEAKER_00] Kod nas doma ili na fejsu

678
00:53:41,280 --> 00:53:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] ili, ono, na nekom predavanju.

679
00:53:43,599 --> 00:53:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] I to je zastrašujuće rijetko,

680
00:53:48,039 --> 00:53:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] što je žalostno,

681
00:53:48,800 --> 00:53:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali meni je bio jedini izbor.

682
00:53:50,619 --> 00:53:51,980
[SPEAKER_01] Jel to ono slobađajuće?

683
00:53:51,980 --> 00:53:53,780
[SPEAKER_00] Je, je.

684
00:53:53,780 --> 00:53:55,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ma prvo, gledaj,

685
00:53:55,260 --> 00:53:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] ja fakat, dakle alpinizam volim,

686
00:53:58,219 --> 00:53:59,219
[SPEAKER_00] samo ne rektalni.

687
00:53:59,619 --> 00:54:02,320
[SPEAKER_00] Meni se penjati na planine fenomenalno

688
00:54:02,320 --> 00:54:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] ili biti u divljini sam.

689
00:54:03,619 --> 00:54:04,800
[SPEAKER_01] Nemogu, zamišljam sad.

690
00:54:04,800 --> 00:54:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovo, ovo, ne, dakle, ono,

691
00:54:07,059 --> 00:54:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] išta, i gdje se ulaži.

692
00:54:08,380 --> 00:54:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] Nemamo opravu za to.

693
00:54:09,619 --> 00:54:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

694
00:54:09,920 --> 00:54:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ma, zvonom, neki su se baš specializirali

695
00:54:12,940 --> 00:54:13,860
[SPEAKER_00] i opet razumijem,

696
00:54:13,860 --> 00:54:16,719
[SPEAKER_00] ok, ali da, ja, ja, ono,

697
00:54:16,719 --> 00:54:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] radije ću izgubiti nekog pratitelja

698
00:54:19,900 --> 00:54:20,559
[SPEAKER_00] nego svoj obraz.

699
00:54:20,559 --> 00:54:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to ne, to jednostavno ne

700
00:54:23,199 --> 00:54:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] i ok mi je to.

701
00:54:24,699 --> 00:54:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ta cijena mi je manja

702
00:54:27,199 --> 00:54:28,760
[SPEAKER_00] nego cijena da ja kalkuliram

703
00:54:28,760 --> 00:54:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] pa da se ne mogu čisto pogledati

704
00:54:30,420 --> 00:54:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju dana.

705
00:54:30,940 --> 00:54:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, uvjetno rečeno je zahtjevno

706
00:54:35,059 --> 00:54:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] jer ima neku svoju cijenu,

707
00:54:36,139 --> 00:54:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne, zapravo je bila lagana odluka.

708
00:54:38,019 --> 00:54:39,619
[SPEAKER_01] Isi imao nekad neke neugodnosti

709
00:54:39,619 --> 00:54:40,619
[SPEAKER_01] u stvarnom životu?

710
00:54:40,619 --> 00:54:42,800
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ne mislim na komentare na Facebooku.

711
00:54:42,800 --> 00:54:43,860
[SPEAKER_00] Misliš danas ili?

712
00:54:43,860 --> 00:54:46,340
[SPEAKER_00] Imam, da, apsolutno sam imao.

713
00:54:46,340 --> 00:54:48,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš to, jel te neko pogodio jajetom nekad?

714
00:54:48,400 --> 00:54:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ili tako nešto?

715
00:54:50,760 --> 00:54:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubitelji lika i dijela Željke Markić

716
00:54:52,699 --> 00:54:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] su palili moje knjige.

717
00:54:53,960 --> 00:54:57,639
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon jednog poavljivanja s njom

718
00:54:57,639 --> 00:54:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] u nekom intervju prije, ne znam,

719
00:54:59,480 --> 00:55:00,639
[SPEAKER_00] deset godina kad je bio onaj,

720
00:55:00,639 --> 00:55:02,480
[SPEAKER_00] jedanest godina kad je bio onaj referendum.

721
00:55:04,300 --> 00:55:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] Znaju se događati jaja,

722
00:55:05,900 --> 00:55:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] jedna, ne želim sad davati ideje ljudima,

723
00:55:08,539 --> 00:55:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] čisto se razumijem,

724
00:55:09,500 --> 00:55:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, najčeš li se to zaustavlja

725
00:55:10,920 --> 00:55:14,699
[SPEAKER_00] na komentarima i ovako

726
00:55:14,699 --> 00:55:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] hvalospjevnim komentarima.

727
00:55:17,159 --> 00:55:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] Što je, dakle, meni je opet ok

728
00:55:19,639 --> 00:55:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] da se nekome nešto ne sviđa

729
00:55:20,980 --> 00:55:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] i to čak dopuštam i na svoj stranici

730
00:55:23,699 --> 00:55:25,260
[SPEAKER_00] da ti kažeš kritiku, da pače,

731
00:55:25,260 --> 00:55:26,139
[SPEAKER_00] kad vrijeđaš.

732
00:55:26,139 --> 00:55:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ili mene, ili moje neistomišljenike.

733
00:55:28,960 --> 00:55:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] To ne dopuštam, recimo.

734
00:55:30,480 --> 00:55:32,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, meni je, onda se ljudi,

735
00:55:32,260 --> 00:55:33,760
[SPEAKER_00] nekad izblokiram ljude.

736
00:55:34,179 --> 00:55:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] Na vas, to je dobro.

737
00:55:35,420 --> 00:55:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer vrijeđa, ono, baš prešli su u granicu

738
00:55:38,000 --> 00:55:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] dobru ustakli, ne slažem se s tobom

739
00:55:39,420 --> 00:55:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] zbog toga, u redu.

740
00:55:40,300 --> 00:55:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] To da kažeš meni, ili mom neistomišljenike,

741
00:55:42,300 --> 00:55:44,659
[SPEAKER_00] ok, ti si govno ovako, onako.

742
00:55:44,659 --> 00:55:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, to nije u redu, niti prema mojoj,

743
00:55:47,000 --> 00:55:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] a uvijek, ono, kontrastrani,

744
00:55:48,340 --> 00:55:49,860
[SPEAKER_00] jer da, čim vrijeđaš, nisi na mojoj strani.

745
00:55:49,860 --> 00:55:50,760
[SPEAKER_00] Točka, doviđenja.

746
00:55:50,760 --> 00:55:54,860
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, bilo je svega i svačega,

747
00:55:54,860 --> 00:55:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] ali fakat ne želim davati ideje

748
00:55:56,760 --> 00:55:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] da se neke od tih stvari ponavljaju.

749
00:55:59,599 --> 00:56:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je i nekih, ono, ozbiljnijih stvari i,

750
00:56:02,539 --> 00:56:07,280
[SPEAKER_00] opet, šutnja nije zlato.

751
00:56:07,280 --> 00:56:09,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kod nekih stvari mislim da je stvar,

752
00:56:09,239 --> 00:56:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo ljudi koji imaju neki javni utjecaj,

753
00:56:10,960 --> 00:56:13,659
[SPEAKER_00] da je korektno opredijeliti se

754
00:56:13,659 --> 00:56:15,320
[SPEAKER_00] i boriti se za ono što smatraš ispravni.

755
00:56:15,320 --> 00:56:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću čak cijeniti one koji to rade,

756
00:56:16,980 --> 00:56:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] čak i ako su na kontrastrani od moje,

757
00:56:18,480 --> 00:56:19,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali to rade dosljedno.

758
00:56:19,559 --> 00:56:23,780
[SPEAKER_00] Cijenim to u smislu da nisu ti rektalci.

759
00:56:23,780 --> 00:56:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] Iako se neću složiti s njima.

760
00:56:26,599 --> 00:56:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da, cijenim to.

761
00:56:28,239 --> 00:56:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] A najgori su mi oni koji imaju jednu lice za javnost,

762
00:56:31,699 --> 00:56:33,840
[SPEAKER_00] jednu za prijatelj, jednu za ženu,

763
00:56:33,840 --> 00:56:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] drugu za ljubavnicu, treće za...

764
00:56:35,659 --> 00:56:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] To je komplicirano, majke ti mile.

765
00:56:38,519 --> 00:56:40,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da zapamtiš kakav si prema svima njima,

766
00:56:40,900 --> 00:56:41,860
[SPEAKER_00] to je stvarno komplicirano.

767
00:56:42,059 --> 00:56:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, ja sam takav kako i jesam,

768
00:56:44,199 --> 00:56:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] neko me se sviđa, neko me se ne sviđa,

769
00:56:45,599 --> 00:56:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] neko me previše glorificira i to mi ide na neku stvar,

770
00:56:47,880 --> 00:56:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] neko me previše spušta to.

771
00:56:49,239 --> 00:56:52,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ako u isti koš staviš i one koji te glorificiraju,

772
00:56:52,820 --> 00:56:57,440
[SPEAKER_00] lako staviš i one koji te previše vrijeđaju,

773
00:56:57,440 --> 00:56:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, ili potpuno nekritički vrijeđaju.

774
00:56:59,420 --> 00:57:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, sve nerealno uvezi mene lako ide u kožno smeće.

775
00:57:02,619 --> 00:57:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] I ono, plus i minus.

776
00:57:03,900 --> 00:57:05,179
[SPEAKER_01] Da, to ti pomaže zapravo.

777
00:57:05,179 --> 00:57:05,539
[SPEAKER_01] Apsolutno.

778
00:57:05,539 --> 00:57:07,460
[SPEAKER_01] Nećeš letiti isto bez veze,

779
00:57:07,579 --> 00:57:09,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali nećeš ni dopustiti da te neko...

780
00:57:09,619 --> 00:57:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] I nećeš se ni raspravljati s njima.

781
00:57:11,199 --> 00:57:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam bio nešto mlađe, onda sam išao objašnjavati.

782
00:57:13,460 --> 00:57:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, nisem ja takav, pa krivo si ništa.

783
00:57:15,400 --> 00:57:17,739
[SPEAKER_00] Čim si nešto fundamentalno krivo shvatio,

784
00:57:17,739 --> 00:57:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] onda svako objašnjavanje ćeš ti doživjeti

785
00:57:19,639 --> 00:57:20,679
[SPEAKER_00] kao nekako izgovaranje,

786
00:57:20,679 --> 00:57:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] ili ono ne prima kritiku.

787
00:57:22,039 --> 00:57:24,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, stari misli, gluposti, u redu.

788
00:57:24,300 --> 00:57:25,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću raditi pametne stvari,

789
00:57:25,480 --> 00:57:27,139
[SPEAKER_00] ti misli, gluposti, meni, u redu.

790
00:57:27,400 --> 00:57:29,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, treba malo i odrasta za to.

791
00:57:29,039 --> 00:57:30,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam trebao.

792
00:57:30,119 --> 00:57:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je neko rođen sa time,

793
00:57:32,699 --> 00:57:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja definitivno nisam bio.

794
00:57:34,440 --> 00:57:35,980
[SPEAKER_00] I ono, prvi put, ne znam,

795
00:57:35,980 --> 00:57:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam pisao za jedan dnevni list,

796
00:57:38,480 --> 00:57:41,940
[SPEAKER_00] ono, cijela Hrvatska to čita.

797
00:57:41,940 --> 00:57:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] I užasno sam glupo reagirao u hrpi situacija,

798
00:57:45,940 --> 00:57:50,760
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam imao tu grešku u koracima,

799
00:57:50,760 --> 00:57:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] u intelektualnim koracima,

800
00:57:51,940 --> 00:57:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] da ljudi sude po činjenicama.

801
00:57:55,519 --> 00:57:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] Neki da, neki ne.

802
00:57:56,420 --> 00:57:57,320
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ja sam mislio,

803
00:57:57,320 --> 00:58:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] ako ja njihovu neku nečinjenicu ispravim

804
00:58:00,039 --> 00:58:01,760
[SPEAKER_00] i kažem, ne, ja sam zapravo to napravio,

805
00:58:01,760 --> 00:58:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] ne ovo što vi kažete,

806
00:58:02,539 --> 00:58:03,760
[SPEAKER_00] da će oni promijeniti svoj stav.

807
00:58:03,760 --> 00:58:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ljudi najčešće samo reinvestiraju

808
00:58:05,599 --> 00:58:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] svoju energiju u ono što žele zaključiti,

809
00:58:07,519 --> 00:58:08,900
[SPEAKER_00] ono što odgovara već u vjerenjima

810
00:58:08,900 --> 00:58:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] koje već imaju.

811
00:58:09,599 --> 00:58:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] O meni, o imigrantima ili o ženama

812
00:58:12,079 --> 00:58:12,820
[SPEAKER_00] ili o bilo čemu.

813
00:58:12,820 --> 00:58:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da sad si štedim energiju,

814
00:58:15,800 --> 00:58:17,820
[SPEAKER_00] a da se nekome ne sviđam,

815
00:58:18,159 --> 00:58:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] nećeš vjerovati ima takvih ljudi,

816
00:58:19,500 --> 00:58:21,219
[SPEAKER_00] nije čak ni tako mali broj,

817
00:58:21,219 --> 00:58:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] ali na susreću ima ovih ljudi

818
00:58:22,659 --> 00:58:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] koji imaju drugačiji stav.

819
00:58:23,500 --> 00:58:25,480
[SPEAKER_01] Da, nećeš vjerovati mene isto ima,

820
00:58:25,480 --> 00:58:26,420
[SPEAKER_01] ima ljudi koji mene ne vole.

821
00:58:26,420 --> 00:58:27,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ko bi rekao?

822
00:58:27,059 --> 00:58:27,460
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ko bi rekao.

823
00:58:27,460 --> 00:58:28,739
[SPEAKER_01] Zamisli ti to, pa nevjerojatno.

824
00:58:28,780 --> 00:58:29,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se tak nekad provodim,

825
00:58:29,840 --> 00:58:30,639
[SPEAKER_01] pa mislim, o Bože,

826
00:58:30,639 --> 00:58:32,420
[SPEAKER_01] pa zar ti ljudi uopće i postakle.

827
00:58:32,420 --> 00:58:35,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ali eto, neka ih tu za neku kontratežu.

828
00:58:35,940 --> 00:58:37,239
[SPEAKER_01] Šta bi rekao,

829
00:58:37,239 --> 00:58:40,179
[SPEAKER_01] živiš život kakav želi živjeti?

830
00:58:40,179 --> 00:58:40,340
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

831
00:58:40,340 --> 00:58:41,179
[SPEAKER_01] Slobodno.

832
00:58:41,179 --> 00:58:41,400
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

833
00:58:41,400 --> 00:58:42,219
[SPEAKER_01] Autentično.

834
00:58:42,219 --> 00:58:42,340
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

835
00:58:42,340 --> 00:58:44,679
[SPEAKER_01] A da ti sad neko da opciju

836
00:58:44,679 --> 00:58:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] da možeš mijenjati recimo lokaciju,

837
00:58:47,539 --> 00:58:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] da li bi,

838
00:58:47,920 --> 00:58:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] evo sad posebno poslje ovih izbora,

839
00:58:49,539 --> 00:58:53,780
[SPEAKER_01] moram se malo samo dotaknuti,

840
00:58:53,780 --> 00:58:55,019
[SPEAKER_01] nije da se nisu dogodili,

841
00:58:55,019 --> 00:58:56,659
[SPEAKER_01] evo imamo najdesniju stranu.

842
00:58:56,659 --> 00:58:57,980
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerojatno.

843
00:58:58,300 --> 00:59:00,739
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerojatno najdesniju vladu i ikada.

844
00:59:00,739 --> 00:59:04,360
[SPEAKER_01] I da bi se ucelio da možeš.

845
00:59:04,360 --> 00:59:05,420
[SPEAKER_00] Pa prvo,

846
00:59:05,420 --> 00:59:07,820
[SPEAKER_00] džumbus,

847
00:59:07,820 --> 00:59:10,760
[SPEAKER_00] hiperkoalicija svih nespojivih,

848
00:59:10,760 --> 00:59:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] nisam siguran da je to idealno.

849
00:59:12,159 --> 00:59:13,719
[SPEAKER_00] Čisto da se razumijemo,

850
00:59:13,719 --> 00:59:15,860
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, to je kao da u neko varivo staviš

851
00:59:15,860 --> 00:59:18,340
[SPEAKER_00] junetinu, grašak, ananas

852
00:59:18,340 --> 00:59:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] i dio drva.

853
00:59:19,460 --> 00:59:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] I nadaš se da će to biti fino.

854
00:59:21,619 --> 00:59:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam.

855
00:59:22,380 --> 00:59:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, koja?

856
00:59:22,940 --> 00:59:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sad smo, ono,

857
00:59:23,980 --> 00:59:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] imamo ovoj drveni stol,

858
00:59:25,059 --> 00:59:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] pa nekom na pamet.

859
00:59:25,820 --> 00:59:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nespojivo je.

860
00:59:27,539 --> 00:59:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da imam dojam

861
00:59:28,400 --> 00:59:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] da to ne bi funkcioniralo

862
00:59:30,219 --> 00:59:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] i da bi to propalo

863
00:59:31,039 --> 00:59:33,579
[SPEAKER_00] najkraće do jeseni.

864
00:59:33,579 --> 00:59:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, prvo neko ideološko pitanje

865
00:59:35,119 --> 00:59:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] da spojiš, ne znam,

866
00:59:36,159 --> 00:59:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] možemo i domovinski pokret i most.

867
00:59:39,059 --> 00:59:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, prvo ideološko pitanje

868
